---
const isSubdomain = Astro.url.hostname === 'trust.openclaw.ai';
const trustHref = isSubdomain ? '/' : '/trust';
const threatModelHref = isSubdomain ? '/threatmodel' : '/trust/threatmodel';

const langLinks = {
  en: { label: 'EN', trust: trustHref, threatmodel: threatModelHref },
  'zh-cn': { label: '中文', trust: isSubdomain ? '/zh-cn' : '/trust/zh-cn', threatmodel: isSubdomain ? '/zh-cn/threatmodel' : '/trust/zh-cn/threatmodel' },
  ko: { label: '한국어', trust: isSubdomain ? '/ko' : '/trust/ko', threatmodel: isSubdomain ? '/ko/threatmodel' : '/trust/ko/threatmodel' },
  ja: { label: '日本語', trust: isSubdomain ? '/ja' : '/trust/ja', threatmodel: isSubdomain ? '/ja/threatmodel' : '/trust/ja/threatmodel' },
};
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <!-- original: <title>Trust - OpenClaw</title> -->
  <title>বিশ্বাস (Trust) - ওপেনক্ল</title>
  <!-- original: <meta name="description" content="OpenClaw Security Program - formal security initiative for AI agents that take real-world actions." /> -->
  <meta name="description" content="ওপেনক্ল সিকিউরিটি প্রোগ্রাম - যেসব এআই এজেন্ট বাস্তব দুনিয়ায় ঘাপলা করতে পারে, তাদের সাইজ করার ফর্মাল উদ্যোগ।" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;1,400&family=Fragment+Mono:ital@0;1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style is:inline>
    :root {
      --primary: #ff5a36;
      --primary-light: #ff8a6b;
      --bg: #ffffff;
      --gray-50: rgb(250,245,244);
      --gray-100: rgb(245,240,239);
      --gray-200: rgb(230,225,224);
      --gray-300: rgb(213,208,207);
      --gray-400: rgb(166,161,160);
      --gray-500: rgb(119,114,113);
      --gray-600: rgb(87,82,81);
      --gray-700: rgb(70,65,64);
      --gray-800: rgb(45,40,38);
      --gray-900: rgb(30,25,24);
      --gray-950: rgb(17,12,11);
      --heading: "DM Sans", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", system-ui, sans-serif;
      --body: "Fragment Mono", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", system-ui, sans-serif;
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { height: 100%; scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      min-height: 100%;
      font-family: var(--body);
      color: var(--gray-500);
      background: var(--bg);
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    ::selection { background: var(--primary); color: #fff; }

    a { color: var(--gray-500); text-decoration: none; }
    a:hover { color: var(--gray-900); }

    /* Topbar */
    .topbar {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      background: var(--bg);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
    }

    .topbar-inner {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 24px;
      height: 52px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .topbar-brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--gray-900);
    }

    .topbar-brand:hover { color: var(--gray-900); }

    .topbar-brand img {
      height: 28px;
      width: auto;
    }

    .topbar-nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
    }

    .topbar-link {
      padding: 6px 14px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-family: var(--heading);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--gray-500);
      transition: color 0.15s, background 0.15s;
    }

    .topbar-link:hover {
      color: var(--gray-900);
      background: var(--gray-50);
    }

    .topbar-link.active {
      color: var(--primary);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .lang-switcher {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 2px;
      margin-left: 8px;
      padding-left: 10px;
      border-left: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
    }

    .lang-link {
      padding: 4px 8px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-family: var(--heading);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--gray-400);
      transition: color 0.15s, background 0.15s;
    }

    .lang-link:hover {
      color: var(--gray-900);
      background: var(--gray-50);
    }

    .lang-link.active {
      color: var(--primary);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 40px 24px;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    .article-header {
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .article-title {
      font-family: var(--heading);
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--gray-900);
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .article-content {
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: var(--gray-600);
    }

    .article-content p:first-child {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--gray-800);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .article-content p {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .article-content .section {
      margin-top: 28px;
    }

    .article-content h2 {
      font-family: var(--heading);
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--gray-900);
      margin-top: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .article-content h3 {
      margin-top: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
      font-family: var(--heading);
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--gray-900);
    }

    .article-content h4 {
      margin-top: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
      font-family: var(--heading);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--gray-800);
    }

    .article-content ul,
    .article-content ol {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      padding-left: 24px;
    }

    .article-content li {
      margin-bottom: 4px;
      padding-left: 8px;
    }

    .article-content li::marker { color: var(--primary); }

    .article-content strong {
      color: var(--gray-800);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .article-content a {
      color: var(--primary);
      text-decoration: underline;
      text-underline-offset: 3px;
    }

    .article-content a:hover { color: var(--gray-900); }

    .article-content code {
      font-family: var(--body);
      font-size: 0.9em;
      padding: 2px 6px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      background: var(--gray-100);
      color: var(--primary);
    }

    .article-content pre {
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: var(--gray-950);
      color: var(--gray-100);
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
      overflow-x: auto;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .article-content pre code {
      padding: 0;
      background: transparent;
      color: inherit;
    }

    .article-content .phases {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 14px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 820px) {
      .article-content .phases { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }

    .article-content .phase {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: var(--bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
    }

    .article-content .phase-num {
      width: 38px;
      height: 38px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #fff;
      background: var(--primary);
      flex: 0 0 auto;
    }

    .article-content .table-wrap {
      overflow-x: auto;
      -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
      margin-top: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .article-content .table-wrap table {
      min-width: 640px;
    }

    .article-content table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
      background: var(--bg);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .article-content th,
    .article-content td {
      padding: 10px 12px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
      vertical-align: top;
      color: var(--gray-600);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .article-content th {
      text-align: left;
      color: var(--gray-900);
      font-weight: 600;
      background: var(--gray-50);
    }

    .article-content .report-box {
      margin-top: 12px;
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border-left: 3px solid var(--primary);
      background: rgba(255,90,54,0.04);
    }

    .article-content .email-display {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 12px;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: var(--gray-950);
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
      font-family: var(--body);
      color: var(--primary);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .article-content .fields {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }

    .article-content .field {
      padding: 6px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--gray-600);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .article-content .checks {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 820px) {
      .article-content .checks { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }

    .article-content .check {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
      background: var(--bg);
    }

    .article-content .check-icon {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: var(--primary);
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      flex: 0 0 auto;
    }

    .article-content .check-icon svg {
      width: 18px;
      height: 18px;
      stroke: #fff !important;
    }

    .article-content .faq-item {
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
      background: var(--bg);
      margin-top: 12px;
    }

    .article-content .faq-q {
      color: var(--gray-900);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .article-content .faq-a { margin-top: 8px; }

    .article-content .cta {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }

    .article-content .btn {
      padding: 10px 16px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--gray-900);
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .article-content .btn:hover {
      background: var(--gray-50);
      border-color: var(--gray-300);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .article-content .btn-primary {
      background: rgba(255,90,54,0.06);
      border-color: rgba(255,90,54,0.25);
    }

    .article-content .btn-primary:hover {
      border-color: var(--primary);
    }

    .article-content footer {
      margin-top: 24px;
      padding-top: 18px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--gray-400);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .article-content footer a {
      color: var(--primary);
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .container { padding: 24px 16px; }
      .topbar-inner { padding: 0 16px; }
      .article-content p:first-child { font-size: 1.1rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="topbar">
    <div class="topbar-inner">
      <a href="https://openclaw.ai" class="topbar-brand">
        <img src="/openclaw-logo-text-dark.png" alt="OpenClaw" />
      </a>
      <div class="topbar-nav">
        <a href={trustHref} class="topbar-link active">Trust</a>
        <a href={threatModelHref} class="topbar-link">Threat Model</a>
        <div class="lang-switcher">
          <a href={langLinks.en.trust} class="lang-link active">{langLinks.en.label}</a>
          <a href={langLinks['zh-cn'].trust} class="lang-link">{langLinks['zh-cn'].label}</a>
          <a href={langLinks.ko.trust} class="lang-link">{langLinks.ko.label}</a>
          <a href={langLinks.ja.trust} class="lang-link">{langLinks.ja.label}</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="container">
    <article class="article">
      <header class="article-header">
        <!-- original: <h1 class="article-title">Trust</h1> -->
        <h1 class="article-title">বিশ্বাস (নাকি বাঁশ)</h1>
      </header>

      <div class="article-content">
        <!-- original: <p>Security posture, roadmap, and how we think about agents that can take real-world actions.</p> -->
        <p>
          সিকিউরিটি, রোডম্যাপ, আর যেসব এআই রিয়েল লাইফে ঘাপলা করতে পারে তাদের নিয়ে আমাদের ফালতু চিন্তাভাবনা।
        </p>

        <section class="section">
          <!-- original: <h2>A New Era in Computing Security</h2> -->
          <h2>কম্পিউটার সিকিউরিটির নতুন যুগ (নতুন প্যারা)</h2>
          <p>For the past 20 years, security models have been built around locking devices and applications down - setting boundaries between inter-process communications, separating internet from local, sandboxing untrusted code. These principles remain important.</p>
          <p>But AI agents represent a fundamental shift.</p>
          <p>Unlike traditional software that does exactly what code tells it to do, AI agents interpret natural language and make decisions about actions. They blur the boundary between user intent and machine execution. They can be manipulated through language itself.</p>
          <p>We understand that with the great utility of a tool like OpenClaw comes great responsibility. Done wrong, an AI agent is a liability. Done right, we can change personal computing for the better.</p>
          <!-- original: <p><strong>This security program exists to get it right.</strong></p> -->
          <p><strong>যাতে কোনো আকাম না হয়, সেজন্যই এই সিকিউরিটি প্রোগ্রামের নাটক।</strong></p>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
          <!-- original: <h2>Context</h2> -->
          <h2>কাহিনী কী (Context)</h2>
          <!-- original: <p>OpenClaw is an AI agent platform. Unlike chatbots that only generate text, OpenClaw agents can:</p> -->
          <p>ওপেনক্ল হলো এআই এজেন্ট প্ল্যাটফর্ম। চ্যাটবটের মতো সারাদিন শুধু প্যাঁচাল না পেরে, ওপেনক্ল এজেন্ট এই কাজগুলো করতে পারে:</p>
          <ul>
            <!-- original: <li>Execute shell commands on the host machine</li> -->
            <li>আপনার মেশিনে বসে শেল কমান্ড মেরে সব ওলটপালট করা</li>
            <!-- original: <li>Send messages through WhatsApp, Telegram, Discord, Slack, and other channels</li> -->
            <li>হোয়াটসঅ্যাপ, টেলিগ্রাম, ডিসকর্ড, স্ল্যাকে আলতু-ফালতু মেসেজ পাঠানো</li>
            <!-- original: <li>Read and write files in the workspace</li> -->
            <li>আপনার সব গোপনীয় ফাইল পড়া আর লেখাআঁকি করা</li>
            <!-- original: <li>Fetch arbitrary URLs from the internet</li> -->
            <li>ইন্টারনেটের যত হাবিজাবি ওয়েবসাইট থেকে ডেটা আনা</li>
            <!-- original: <li>Schedule automated tasks</li> -->
            <li>নিজে নিজেই কাজ করার নামে ঘুমিয়ে থাকা</li>
            <!-- original: <li>Access connected services and APIs</li> -->
            <li>সব ধরনের এপিআই (API) আর সার্ভিসে নাক গলানো</li>
          </ul>
          <!-- original: <p>This capability is what makes OpenClaw useful. It's also what makes security critical.</p> -->
          <p>এই ক্ষমতার জন্যই ওপেনক্ল কাজের জিনিস। আর এই কারণেই সিকিউরিটির এমন বেহাল দশা।</p>
          <!-- original: <p>AI agents that can take real-world actions introduce risks that traditional software doesn't have:</p> -->
          <p>যেসব এআই রিয়েল লাইফে আকাম করতে পারে, তাদের সাধারণ সফটওয়্যারের চেয়ে বেশি প্যারা আছে:</p>
          <ol>
            <!-- original: <li><strong>Prompt injection</strong> - Malicious users can craft messages that manipulate the AI into performing unintended actions</li> -->
            <li><strong>প্রম্পট ইঞ্জেকশন</strong> - দুষ্ট লোকজন এআইকে বোকা বানিয়ে উল্টাপাল্টা কাজ করাতে পারে (মানুষের মতো)।</li>
            <!-- original: <li><strong>Indirect injection</strong> - Malicious content in fetched URLs, emails, or documents can hijack agent behavior</li> -->
            <li><strong>ইনডাইরেক্ট ইঞ্জেকশন</strong> - বাইরের ওয়েবসাইটের হাবিজাবি বা ইমেইল দিয়ে এজেন্টের মাথা খারাপ করা।</li>
            <!-- original: <li><strong>Tool abuse</strong> - Even without injection, misconfigured agents can cause damage through overly permissive settings</li> -->
            <li><strong>টুল অ্যাবিউজ</strong> - কোনো ইঞ্জেকশন ছাড়াই, পারমিশন বেশি দিলে এজেন্ট নিজেই সব ধ্বংস করে দিতে পারে।</li>
            <!-- original: <li><strong>Identity risks</strong> - Agents can send messages as you, potentially damaging relationships or reputation</li> -->
            <li><strong>আইডেন্টিটি রিস্ক</strong> - এজেন্ট আপনার নামে মেসেজ পাঠিয়ে আপনার মান-সম্মান ডুবিয়ে দিতে পারে।</li>
          </ol>
          <!-- original: <p>These aren't theoretical. They're documented attack patterns that affect all AI agent systems.</p> -->
          <p>এগুলা কোনো ভাওতাবাজি না। এগুলো আসল অ্যাটাক প্যাটার্ন, যা সব এআই সিস্টেমের বারোটা বাজায়।</p>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
          <h2>Scope</h2>
          <p>This security program covers the entire OpenClaw ecosystem. <strong>Nothing is out of scope.</strong></p>

          <h4>Core Platform</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>OpenClaw CLI and Gateway (<code>openclaw</code>)</li>
            <li>Agent execution engine</li>
            <li>Tool implementations</li>
            <li>Channel integrations (WhatsApp, Telegram, Discord, Slack, Signal, etc.)</li>
          </ul>

          <h4>Applications</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>macOS desktop application</li>
            <li>iOS mobile application</li>
            <li>Android mobile application</li>
            <li>Web interface</li>
          </ul>

          <h4>Services</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>ClawHub (clawhub.ai) - Skills marketplace and registry</li>
            <li>Documentation (docs.openclaw.ai)</li>
            <li>Any hosted infrastructure</li>
          </ul>

          <h4>Extensions</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Official extensions (<code>extensions/</code>)</li>
            <li>Plugin SDK and third-party plugins</li>
            <li>Skills distributed through ClawHub</li>
          </ul>

          <h4>People</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Core maintainers and contributors</li>
            <li>Security processes and response procedures</li>
            <li>Supply chain and dependency management</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
          <h2>Program Overview</h2>
          <p>We're establishing a formal security function with four phases:</p>

          <div class="phases">
